  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "Mix the rolled oats, chopped onion, and a pinch of black pepper in a bowl. Drizzle with olive oil.",
    "Spread the mixture evenly on a baking sheet and bake for about 20 minutes until golden brown.",
    "In a separate pan, heat chicken or vegetable broth over medium heat. Add finely chopped garlic and lemon juice, stir well.",
